    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私って怖いんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどうしたんだ？　何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 4.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それが……SNSに「一ノ瀬怜は性格がきつくて\n怒ると怖そう」って書かれていたんです",
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それくらいならたまに見かけるので\n気にしないようにしてるんですが、今回は……",
      "startTime": 20.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "「サニピのメンバーも一ノ瀬怜を怖がって\nいつも気を遣っていそう」とまで書かれていて……",
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私ってそんなに怖そうに見えますか？",
      "startTime": 32.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜はクールで気が強いイメージがあるから\nきつい印象を持たれやすいのかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが思ってるほど私はクールじゃありません\n現に今もこうして気にしてるんですから",
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}